<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmaci√≥n de Pedido</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #E0E0E0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #1E1E1E;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E1E1E 0%, #2A2A2A 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFA500 0%, #FF8C00 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #B0B0B0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .order-info {
            background-color: #252525;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .order-info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .order-info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .label {
            color: #B0B0B0;
        }
        .value {
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .items-table th {
            background-color: #252525;
            color: #B0B0B0;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .items-table td {
            padding: 15px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            color: #E0E0E0;
        }
        .items-table tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .item-name {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        .item-quantity {
            color: #B0B0B0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .item-price {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #FFA500;
        }
        .totals {
            background-color: #252525;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .total-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .total-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-top: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .total-row.final {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .total-row.final .label {
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        .total-row.final .value {
            color: #FFA500;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFA500 0%, #FF8C00 100%);
            color: #FFFFFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.4);
        }
        .estimated-time {
            background-color: #252525;
            border-left: 4px solid #FFA500;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .estimated-time p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #E0E0E0;
        }
        .estimated-time strong {
            color: #FFA500;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #1A1A1A;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .footer p {
            color: #808080;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #FFA500;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            .items-table th,
            .items-table td {
                padding: 10px 8px;
                font-size: 13px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üçΩÔ∏è</div>
            <h1>¬°Pedido Confirmado!</h1>
            <p>Gracias por tu compra</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hola {{customerName}},</p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 30px; color: #B0B0B0;">
                Tu pedido ha sido confirmado y est√° siendo preparado con mucho cuidado.
            </p>
            
            <div class="order-info">
                <div class="order-info-row">
                    <span class="label">N√∫mero de Pedido:</span>
                    <span class="value">#{{orderId}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="order-info-row">
                    <span class="label">Fecha:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{orderDate}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="section-title">Detalle del Pedido</h2>
            <table class="items-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Producto</th>
                        <th style="text-align: center;">Cant.</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Precio</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each items}}
                    <tr>
                        <td class="item-name">{{this.nombre}}</td>
                        <td class="item-quantity">{{this.cantidad}}</td>
                        <td class="item-price">${{this.precio}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>
            
            <div class="totals">
                <div class="total-row">
                    <span class="label">Subtotal:</span>
                    <span class="value">${{subtotal}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="total-row final">
                    <span class="label">Total:</span>
                    <span class="value">${{total}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if estimatedTime}}
            <div class="estimated-time">
                <p><strong>Tiempo estimado:</strong> {{estimatedTime}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <center>
                <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="cta-button">Seguir mi Pedido</a>
            </center>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #B0B0B0; font-size: 14px;">
                Si tienes alguna pregunta sobre tu pedido, no dudes en contactarnos.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© 2026 Restaurant. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="#">Pol√≠tica de Privacidad</a> | 
                <a href="#">T√©rminos de Servicio</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
